PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Toilet Paper Trading App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the toilet paper trading app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app connects toilet paper buyers and sellers in a user-friendly marketplace. Users can list their surplus rolls, browse available inventory, and complete secure transactions for toilet paper exchange or purchase.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Is it safe to trade toilet paper through the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes, we prioritize user safety and hygiene. All traded toilet paper must be unopened and in its original packaging. We also provide guidelines for safe meetups and contactless delivery options.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I make money selling toilet paper on the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: While the app's primary purpose is to facilitate toilet paper exchange during shortages, users can set their own prices. However, we encourage fair pricing and discourage price gouging to maintain a helpful community.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: What makes your app different from buying toilet paper in stores?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Our app offers a unique solution during supply shortages, allowing users to find toilet paper when stores are out of stock. It also promotes community sharing and can be a more convenient option for those unable to visit multiple stores.
